# Design System Rules (mandatory)

**Every UI change MUST use the design system.** Read `docs/design-system.md` before editing components.

## SSoT order

1. `src/styles/tokens.css` — new colors, spacing, sizes
2. `src/app/globals.css` — `@theme inline` wiring only
3. `src/lib/design-system/` — `layout`, `chrome`, `typography` recipes
4. `src/components/ui/` — shadcn primitives
5. Feature components — compose recipes; no raw values

## Required imports

- `cn` from `@/lib/utils`
- `layout`, `chrome`, `typography` from `@/lib/design-system`
- UI primitives from `@/components/ui/*`
- Site/nav from `@/config/site`, `@/config/navigation`

## Forbidden in feature components

- Hardcoded colors (`#hex`, `oklch()`, `rgb()`, `hsl()`)
- Arbitrary Tailwind when a token/recipe exists (`text-[10px]`, `h-14`, `min-h-128`, `px-6` for chrome/panels)
- Duplicating island styles — use `layout.surfaceIsland`, `layout.bodyIsland`, `chrome.*`
- Custom Button/Card duplicates of shadcn

## When a recipe is missing

1. Add token to `tokens.css`
2. Wire in `globals.css` `@theme inline`
3. Add recipe to `layout.ts`, `chrome.ts`, or `typography.ts`
4. Use the recipe in the component

## shadcn

- Style: `base-nova` per `components.json`
- Add: `bunx shadcn@latest add <name> -y`
- `"use client"` only on interactive primitives

## Content

- Types: `src/types/content.ts`
- Blog MDX: `typography.prose` + `blog-prose` on post body
- Query blog data via `src/lib/blog/queries.ts`
- MDX embeds: `src/components/content/mdx/` — register in `src/mdx-components.tsx`

